flowchart TB
  HOOKS[CLI lifecycle hooks<br/>SessionStart / Stop / SessionEnd]
  CODEX[Codex CLI / Desktop<br/>rollout JSONL]
  SCAN[每日全量增量扫描<br/>分块 / token / 审计]
  USER[交互入口]

  INJECT[上下文构建与注入]
  READ[dev-memory-read<br/>定位与搜索]
  CAPTURE[dev-memory-capture<br/>写入与纠错]
  SETUP[dev-memory-setup<br/>整理未分类内容]
  TIDY[dev-memory-tidy<br/>批量校准]
  GRAD[dev-memory-graduate<br/>上提与归档]
  CLI[dev-memory-cli<br/>统一执行入口]

  REPO[repo/<br/>跨分支共享记忆]
  BRANCH[branches/&lt;branch&gt;/<br/>分支工作记忆]
  ARCHIVE[branches/_archived/<br/>已归档分支]

  HOOKS --> INJECT
  CODEX --> SCAN
  SCAN --> CLI
  INJECT --> REPO
  INJECT --> BRANCH
  USER --> READ
  USER --> CAPTURE
  USER --> SETUP
  USER --> TIDY
  USER --> GRAD
  READ --> CLI
  CAPTURE --> CLI
  SETUP --> CLI
  TIDY --> CLI
  GRAD --> CLI
  CLI --> REPO
  CLI --> BRANCH
  CLI --> ARCHIVE

